shift galaxies expected from detailed studies of the stellar masses and\nmass profiles of their low-redshift descendants, and from models of turbulent\ngas fragmentation. This may be the first direct constraint on the IMF in a lens\nat z = 1.5, which is not a cluster central galaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Mar 2017 19:00:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-29"}
