imity of the Fe\n$t_{2}$ van Hove singularity to the Fermi level and the sensitive dependence of\nits position on external conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Mar 2017 11:39:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-26"}
